            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EA%20sad%20Christian%20is%20no%20witness%20for%20God.%20Ezra%20read%20the%20Book%20of%20the%20Law%20to%20the%20Jewish%20remnant%2C%20and%20when%20they%20heard%20God's%20words%2C%20%22all%20the%20people%20chanted%2C%20%E2%80%98Amen!%20Amen!'%20as%20they%20lifted%20their%20hands%20toward%20heaven.%20Then%20they%20bowed%20down%20and%20worshiped%20the%20Lord%20with%20their%20faces%20to%20the%20ground%22%20(Nehemiah%208%3A6).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhy%20should%20church%20services%20and%20times%20of%20preaching%20be%20times%20of%20sadness%20and%20boredom%3F%20When%20the%20people%20wept%20after%20hearing%20God's%20words%2C%20Nehemiah%20told%20them%2C%20%22Go%20and%20celebrate%20with%20a%20feast%20of%20choice%20foods%20and%20sweet%20drinks%2C%20and%20share%20gifts%20of%20food%20with%20people%20who%20have%20nothing%20prepared%22%20(v.%2010).%20The%20Israelites%20obeyed%20and%20celebrated%20%22with%20great%20joy%20because%20they%20had%20heard%20God's%20words%20and%20understood%20them%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E(v.%2012)%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELater%20that%20month%2C%20in%20celebrating%20a%20major%20festival%20that%20had%20been%20unobserved%20for%20many%20years%2C%20the%20people%20lived%20in%20booths%20for%20seven%20days%2C%20and%20%22everyone%20was%20filled%20with%20great%20joy%22%20(v.%2017).%20Another%20observance%20followed%2C%20and%20this%20time%20for%20six%20hours%20at%20a%20time%20the%20Levites%20led%20in%20worship%2C%20saying%2C%20%22Stand%20up%20and%20praise%20the%20Lord%20your%20God%2C%20for%20he%20lives%20from%20everlasting%20to%20everlasting!%22%20Then%20they%20continued%2C%20%22Praise%20his%20glorious%20name!%20It%20is%20far%20greater%20than%20we%20can%20think%20or%20say%22%20(9%3A5).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhy%20should%20Christians%20ever%20lose%20their%20joy%3F%20Someone%20has%20said%20that%20if%20the%20devil%20can't%20steal%20your%20joy%2C%20he%20can't%20spoil%20your%20goods.%20Even%20in%20your%20most%20difficult%20moments%2C%20look%20to%20eternity%2C%20where%20you%20will%20forever%20rejoice%2C%20world%20without%20end.%20Take%20a%20drink%20today%20from%20the%20joy%20of%20heaven%2C%20for%20it%20is%20your%20strength!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
