            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Corinthians%209%3A1-18%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_1%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Corinthians%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EPaul%20Gives%20Up%20His%20Rights%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EAm%20I%20not%20as%20free%20as%20anyone%20else%3F%20Am%20I%20not%20an%20apostle%3F%20Haven%26%23x2019%3Bt%20I%20seen%20Jesus%20our%20Lord%20with%20my%20own%20eyes%3F%20Isn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20it%20because%20of%20my%20work%20that%20you%20belong%20to%20the%20Lord%3F%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_2%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EEven%20if%20others%20think%20I%20am%20not%20an%20apostle%2C%20I%20certainly%20am%20to%20you.%20You%20yourselves%20are%20proof%20that%20I%20am%20the%20Lord%26%23x2019%3Bs%20apostle.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_3%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20my%20answer%20to%20those%20who%20question%20my%20authority.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20%3Cem%3Ethose%20who%20examine%20me.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_4%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20we%20have%20the%20right%20to%20live%20in%20your%20homes%20and%20share%20your%20meals%3F%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_5%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20we%20have%20the%20right%20to%20bring%20a%20believing%20wife%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A5a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20%3Cem%3Ea%20sister%20a%20wife.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20with%20us%20as%20the%20other%20apostles%20and%20the%20Lord%26%23x2019%3Bs%20brothers%20do%2C%20and%20as%20Peter%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A5b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Greek%20%3Cem%3ECephas.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20does%3F%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_6%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EOr%20is%20it%20only%20Barnabas%20and%20I%20who%20have%20to%20work%20to%20support%20ourselves%3F%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_7%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EWhat%20soldier%20has%20to%20pay%20his%20own%20expenses%3F%20What%20farmer%20plants%20a%20vineyard%20and%20doesn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20have%20the%20right%20to%20eat%20some%20of%20its%20fruit%3F%20What%20shepherd%20cares%20for%20a%20flock%20of%20sheep%20and%20isn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20allowed%20to%20drink%20some%20of%20the%20milk%3F%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_8%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EAm%20I%20expressing%20merely%20a%20human%20opinion%2C%20or%20does%20the%20law%20say%20the%20same%20thing%3F%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_9%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20the%20law%20of%20Moses%20says%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BYou%20must%20not%20muzzle%20an%20ox%20to%20keep%20it%20from%20eating%20as%20it%20treads%20out%20the%20grain.%26%23x201D%3B%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Deut%2025%3A4.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Was%20God%20thinking%20only%20about%20oxen%20when%20he%20said%20this%3F%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_10%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EWasn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20he%20actually%20speaking%20to%20us%3F%20Yes%2C%20it%20was%20written%20for%20us%2C%20so%20that%20the%20one%20who%20plows%20and%20the%20one%20who%20threshes%20the%20grain%20might%20both%20expect%20a%20share%20of%20the%20harvest.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_11%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3ESince%20we%20have%20planted%20spiritual%20seed%20among%20you%2C%20aren%26%23x2019%3Bt%20we%20entitled%20to%20a%20harvest%20of%20physical%20food%20and%20drink%3F%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_12%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20you%20support%20others%20who%20preach%20to%20you%2C%20shouldn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20we%20have%20an%20even%20greater%20right%20to%20be%20supported%3F%20But%20we%20have%20never%20used%20this%20right.%20We%20would%20rather%20put%20up%20with%20anything%20than%20be%20an%20obstacle%20to%20the%20Good%20News%20about%20Christ.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_13%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20you%20realize%20that%20those%20who%20work%20in%20the%20temple%20get%20their%20meals%20from%20the%20offerings%20brought%20to%20the%20temple%3F%20And%20those%20who%20serve%20at%20the%20altar%20get%20a%20share%20of%20the%20sacrificial%20offerings.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_14%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20the%20same%20way%2C%20the%20Lord%20ordered%20that%20those%20who%20preach%20the%20Good%20News%20should%20be%20supported%20by%20those%20who%20benefit%20from%20it.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_15%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EYet%20I%20have%20never%20used%20any%20of%20these%20rights.%20And%20I%20am%20not%20writing%20this%20to%20suggest%20that%20I%20want%20to%20start%20now.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20would%20rather%20die%20than%20lose%20my%20right%20to%20boast%20about%20preaching%20without%20charge.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_16%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EYet%20preaching%20the%20Good%20News%20is%20not%20something%20I%20can%20boast%20about.%20I%20am%20compelled%20by%20God%20to%20do%20it.%20How%20terrible%20for%20me%20if%20I%20didn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20preach%20the%20Good%20News!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_17%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20I%20were%20doing%20this%20on%20my%20own%20initiative%2C%20I%20would%20deserve%20payment.%20But%20I%20have%20no%20choice%2C%20for%20God%20has%20given%20me%20this%20sacred%20trust.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22cor1_9_18%22%20bk%3D%22cor1%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EWhat%20then%20is%20my%20pay%3F%20It%20is%20the%20opportunity%20to%20preach%20the%20Good%20News%20without%20charging%20anyone.%20That%26%23x2019%3Bs%20why%20I%20never%20demand%20my%20rights%20when%20I%20preach%20the%20Good%20News.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E"
